{"tid":1378493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞青衣比搞香港任何地方都更加危險, 千其唔好中伏","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:16:44.000Z","uid":44139,"like":316,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"843516e8f29fcc63a52e037dd361bf5b6ea48528","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"講緊呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377215/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377215/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n住青衣/係青衣南返工既都知道, 要去青衣南只有一條過既青衣路, 而去青衣西部船廠更加只有一條有入無出既西草灣路, 班差佬只要頭尾封好青衣路就會都走唔到, 係完全唔需要開槍, 所以就算有幾多油庫都好都唔會怕<br />\n<br />\nQ. 實有的士同小巴走既~<br />\nA. 小巴得一架88G, 班次超少, 仲要差佬一停車實捉到你, 的士更加唔洗講, 因為的士佬係唔會專登入去, 入油都有美景同青衣西路<br />\n<br />\nQ. 行海邊走咪得囉<br />\nA. 比你行到去青馬大橋橋底, 要行上去青衣北係無可能, 雖然地圖係見到有路, 但其實係好高既天橋, 唔會上到去, 而青衣東南更係貨櫃碼頭, 去到近藍澄灣都唔會行到海邊<br />\n<br />\nQ. 行唔到海邊咪行上山囉<br />\nA. Sor, 自然徑同青衣南係完全無連接, 再加上當年玫瑰園計劃一早將個邊既山整靚好, 所以比你見到有自然徑都唔會行到上去<br />\n<br />\nQ. 無路走咁我行出去游水咪得囉?<br />\nA. 你最近游到上岸既地方起碼有一公里, 仲要係昂船洲大橋橋底, 上左岸之後又係無公共交通同得一條路走, 再加上水警行動基地就係長沙灣, 開去藍巴勒海峽絕對快過你游水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論: 青衣最多可以搞青衣城個頭, 但青衣南油庫一定中伏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7657df6e82b09c215f760e6cc151f4d8e9df390","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":113,"dislike":0,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMmTQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMmTQy.png&h=eb522ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我畫埋比大家睇, 事實真係得呢條路(紅線), 係唔會有其他路走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00c7c5a0d98ff934018bf805ad13831cbf1ac2f","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"推呀, 唔好見到成四千幾個正評去送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522fea3d6c07a2d06f2858cc5e179f511fe17f11","tid":1378493,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5ed9585884fb281f23ba147b77b764399f63dfd5","tid":1378493,"uid":276834,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"我補充，青衣通往荃灣嘅橋雖然有條小路上直到海濱花園，但勁易被封鎖，幾隻狗就封到。"},{"pid":"098013e136a42f257566bf07a35070743ea12c83","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed573c7a5070a7b92b1bc1d607e6f69c86047a1","tid":1378493,"uid":221518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"Agger 喺嗰度搞極難走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dbd90633e5a998daf933f9fadf04988d73ca76","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c25bc0edd2dc053249eab4c5b724293e049e97d","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"小巴係88M先係, 88G最多去到藍澄灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0cfff63c6453c53f663e1bd2e3712dd4c054d1","tid":1378493,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2119ec2d6bea387ab41680b82bddf227e48dd9d7","tid":1378493,"uid":247808,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"到時唔熟路又封曬點走<br />\n利申 青衣居民都大多數唔會去油庫附近"},{"pid":"be6317292dac02dadca682008838057c259009d6","tid":1378493,"uid":129733,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n補充原因<br />\n1：地型<br />\n油庫同市區只靠2條陸路連接，易入難走<br />\n水路碼頭位於市中心，油庫碼頭你入唔到去，入到都冇船到<br />\n去葵芳汀九青馬嘅路都位處山腰，體力再好搏鬥完再上去散水都要好耐<br />\n山路不可行，因為油庫對住嘅山坡係高3百米嘅峭壁，冇山徑入口，一係爬石一係爆林直上3百米，然而座山俗稱叫3支香，即係有3個山峰，一上一落就算唔累死警狗已經喺落山口等你<br />\n<br />\n2：潛在危險<br />\n油庫爆足以摧毀島南<br />\n到時手足同狗狗一齊死，島南平民陪葬，等同恐襲<br />\n<br />\n3：交通問題<br />\n得5條橋2條鐵，封咗橋有義載都冇用<br />\n<br />\n4：島上值得示威嘅地方唔多<br />\n青衣城狗鐵中心<br />\n警狗宿舍<br />\n藍澄灣支那人酒店<br />\n<br />\n我認為青衣只適做荃葵青嘅中途站，遊行去完4嘅地點就要去下站<br />\n否則留守衝突弊多於利<br />\n<br />\n利申埋住過晒荃葵青返過晒島南北，荃葵比較好散水<br />\n島南嘅路僻到行幾多次都覺陌生同陰森"},{"pid":"fd614a4792bd850d664b3e157d2ce689641b3e0f","tid":1378493,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02ecfc0de7966fb40a315c249c8b7c470afdcfb8","tid":1378493,"uid":39860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9b0d3d9b3b2c0167b9ab04fad6a4391162e05e4e","tid":1378493,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"孤島入去送死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a577015a5df723aa1644c5d8c057e0ebca76d886","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2119ec2d6bea387ab41680b82bddf227e48dd9d7","tid":1378493,"uid"