citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"封曬冇得走 仲要得幾條樓<br />\n到時候真係變左孤島求生"},{"pid":"a113313ba0aec1b08b8d1f25570160c206d8d3ae","tid":1378493,"uid":289686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92044f8c971dc4850dfe8dc588f478210d08dd12","tid":1378493,"uid":290941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7aa7deebfccbf3239763502c1ab2d88bc44374f0","tid":1378493,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e568e04a8b9c63482b7cecf072eda8f2923d592","tid":1378493,"uid":187387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"大家唔好遮眼見到有人發放策略就盲目正評"},{"pid":"d1dd0cb29e440ce916c9cc7633822a218f44bcfc","tid":1378493,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e568e04a8b9c63482b7cecf072eda8f2923d592","tid":1378493,"uid":187387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"大家唔好遮眼見到有人發放策略就盲目正評"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"青衣/油庫絕地唔係好地方"},{"pid":"83d6c90cc04f0979b1846a69766738575a53dbe5","tid":1378493,"uid":239205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"住青衣廿幾年 青衣冇光復價值 深黃多過藍 雖然有村 但佢地唔會敢做野 佢地一打人 青衣大把深黃日日招呼 唔好為浪費資源係青衣 再加上青衣真係冇路走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eca6147de2e6576f33478eb75e1bca18c2eecf","tid":1378493,"uid":267208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2fa13ae2fc0bfc3e2d3afdb1b8061ae6b029280","tid":1378493,"uid":168472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce2597af1d043fef3dc6987ea1dccaef50f03158","tid":1378493,"uid":168472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b3353ef368b1f9244b67d1e77dc20a92cea02ec","tid":1378493,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"要搞青衣不如直接搞和你飛第2集仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef779771ea0ace0f4d75d5a4a1e9d1b2510673ac","tid":1378493,"uid":263181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:12:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n事先check地形真係好重要"},{"pid":"dbfd981a3e21bc0e07bc9b9e27e603095a973047","tid":1378493,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:15:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>逃生路線</strong><br />\n青衣得4個方法走到 <br />\n1) 地鐵 東涌線 機場快線<br />\n個人建議走機場快線入機場 (15分鐘左右) 再搭機場巴士走，方便全港九人士返屋企，同埋就算走唔到都入到機場避避<br />\n但一封站或者飛青衣就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 南北橋<br />\n南橋可以去葵芳再走<br />\n北橋(青衣連儂橋個邊)可以直去荃灣，或者跑去海濱花園再走<br />\n一封哂兩條橋就得返條好窄既行人路行到，一多人走就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 油庫青衣路經青衣西路同長青公路入汀九青馬 或者 經青沙公路入昂船洲<br />\n但你一定要有車，加上青衣路好撚窄(2條行車線)<br />\n你一多人走就塞硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 水路<br />\n青衣有個好細嘅碼頭作小型船隻泊岸上落客，但首先你要準備好船隻for走佬<br />\n<br />\n冇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係你入山<br />\n平時楓樹窩路塞車啲青衣居民都已經走唔到，你仲要咁多人入青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>青衣勢力</strong><br />\n青衣有個好大嘅警署 (葵青警區總部, 藍白間) 同黑警宿舍 (杏色, 有A B座)<br />\n<img src=\"https://mapio.net/images-p/70293445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmapio.net%2Fimages-p%2F70293445.jpg&h=46d6ccb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再過少少就有涌美村、大王下村、楓樹窩村、藍田村 、鹽田角村等鄧氏同陳氏原居民村<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/images/elections_1115/tsingyi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Frre%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Felections_1115%2Ftsingyi.pdf&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=5f9c77ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/images/elections_1115/tsingyi.pdf</a><br />\n再黎長青村一帶好撚多廢老，長亨長宏比較多新移民<br />\n另外藍澄灣個3間酒店經常有支那人入住，所以青衣城成日都有好多支那人問點去酒店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論</strong><br />\n入青衣=困獸鬥<br />\n雖然青衣好多深黃 (好多謝你地守護青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一日未諗到方法可以比大量示威者安全離開青衣，一日都唔好諗係青衣到示威<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做足功課好緊要</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d7364c10a0320f6d62ca532136e0cc02025115e6","tid":1378493,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:31:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>重申五大訴求<br />\n1.全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)<br />\n</strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港 時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"09c39924f547fdadcd2a9410dd216e70425ed84e","tid":1378493,"uid":269695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f988e5c0e093c6646ce84aaecb3e1d5a5e0b9bdd","tid":1378493,"uid":278875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9277c124504b0db411cd4c9716a8ed86f5bab9fb","tid":1378493,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee238148caa028df0f17fa1507bd339daff6f3a","tid":1378493,"uid":259199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b840bde2cc882e78f91e25ad8f6d5ebede7386de","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237d8ca2fb147441a40b70e643ce0ff4fdd72257","tid":1378493,"uid":260909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:49:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2eab362ecfb4f5e4209e1866e004ccc68f9b2fa6","tid":1378493,"uid":100344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e94fece838fcbd144e2008f7233bac79f692cb","tid":1378493,"uid":148989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560c1fbbbbcbe964f662ece7dc7494104b21c37e","tid":1378493,"uid":50699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fedb8529e907af324e936e0f1c5530b495d8e04","tid":1378493,"uid":110589,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"青衣油庫真係唔好搞 絕對係一個孤島<br />\n只要一封南北橋&amp;狗鐵<br />\n青衣就唔會有路走<br />\n油庫果邊位置近青馬橋 極遠離民居 <br />\n甚至我敢形容果個位可以話係零交通 <br />\n路就得一條 基本啲狗前後一包抄<br />\n煙都唔撚洗出一粒 大家就送頭比人扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 住左係青衣29年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"同意,PS住青衣21年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:52:56.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n利申住青衣20年"},{"pid":"12adb3fb83b4037d071c7dcc75f16b316ed87130","tid":1378493,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df5af63d79dfc6608358909c80c4f39599a53bc4","tid":1378493,"uid":70834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"荃灣"},{"pid":"0643a14f185eb8e553971f749661c3293a1b9dc4","tid":1378493,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:54:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5ace3277110caf81aaa07876de3effa71ea7729","tid":1378493,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:23:10.000Z","msg":"仲有啲on9推嗰個post <br />\n推依個啦！！"},{"pid":"628d244c31208c5d1ea846cf1ca611dc00ffdb57","tid":1378493,"uid":229296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:25:08.000Z","msg":"推，青衣真係好易搞死自已，鐵路一停就仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n_____________________________<br />\n8月5 我會罷工！一齊罷工！"},{"pid":"3d76ffad2f42c901ba44071450c1718964ee1139","tid":1378493,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b97ff78c60bc2a2b72472e616066cc33426d9f","tid":1378493,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:27:31.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"91b252a1d1438b61c5de1fddee31c7ef114577b7","tid":1378493,"uid":135288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:28:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人完全唔睇cm就正皮咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a500cfe7daf5d61e0a0d4fa92551c5ba2b3efd7","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5306b43604e4020301cc1191ad948d8248893f03","tid":1378493,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"push."},{"pid":"89c1c12ac7352d7535a4ba724354d20a0a3b06a9","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29994415a369457fde6cc603d689874c52dc8b1","tid":1378493,"uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:27:22.000Z","msg":"地圖都未識睇就就話搞青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d20ba252823369014c479ce0eeea7bb9f1f7d35","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a78e92a231ba495058d9b9acbc18ede346338e1","tid":1378493,"uid":78084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:16:18.000Z","msg":"除非直接佔領，封晒五條橋<br />\n斷入機場馬灣嘅路<br />\n但都係有啲魯莽草率"},{"pid":"a73f27a06dfb530eeedfaab9258560e11064e880","tid":1378493,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4b4bcbb12590f35fe77004247d4541b92a73966","tid":1378493,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"青衣地形惡劣<br />\n有如之前有人提出入將軍澳工業邨圍CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9080b0e71882c9ea1464ece9150b65f93ae00800","tid":1378493,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbfd981a3e21bc0e07bc9b9e27e603095a973047","tid":1378493,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:15:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>逃生路線</strong><br />\n青衣得4個方法走到 <br />\n1) 地鐵 東涌線 機場快線<br />\n個人建議走機場快線入機場 (15分鐘左右) 再搭機場巴士走，方便全港九人士返屋企，同埋就算走唔到都入到機場避避<br />\n但一封站或者飛青衣就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 南北橋<br />\n南橋可以去葵芳再走<br />\n北橋(青衣連儂橋個邊)可以直去荃灣，或者跑去海濱花園再走<br />\n一封哂兩條橋就得返條好窄既行人路行到，一多人走就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 油庫青衣路經青衣西路同長青公路入汀九青馬 或者 經青沙公路入昂船洲<br />\n但你一定要有車，加上青衣路好撚窄(2條行車線)<br />\n你一多人走就塞硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 水路<br />\n青衣有個好細嘅碼頭作小型船隻泊岸上落客，但首先你要準備好船隻for走佬<br />\n<br />\n冇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係你入山<br />\n平時楓樹窩路塞車啲青衣居民都已經走唔到，你仲要咁多人入青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>青衣勢力</strong><br />\n青衣有個好大嘅警署 (葵青警區總部, 藍白間) 同黑警宿舍 (杏色, 有A B座)<br />\n<img src=\"https://mapio.net/images-p/70293445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmapio.net%2Fimages-p%2F70293445.jpg&h=46d6ccb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再過少少就有涌美村、大王下村、楓樹窩村、藍田村 、鹽田角村等鄧氏同陳氏原居民村<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/images/elections_1115/tsingyi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Frre%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Felections_1115%2Ftsingyi.pdf&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=5f9c77ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/images/elections_1115/tsingyi.pdf</a><br />\n再黎長青村一帶好撚多廢老，長亨長宏比較多新移民<br />\n另外藍澄灣個3間酒店經常有支那人入住，所以青衣城成日都有好多支那人問點去酒店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論</strong><br />\n入青衣=困獸鬥<br />\n雖然青衣好多深黃 (好多謝你地守護青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一日未諗到方法可以比大量示威者安全離開青衣，一日都唔好諗係青衣到示威<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做足功課好緊要</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"莫講話大量示威者 青衣而家多小小人離開都塞到仆街 好多地方整路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入青衣實元氣大傷"},{"pid":"89ac0043790fd33c4f255f590c18f87832e1018b","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b805c1e1162b5c9cff5b9e47a39e7f88582fbd08","tid":1378493,"uid":6661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13c36ceb1686fb9305cbc1bfbdccfa0cfb6010ed","tid":1378493,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31c6c34e46e8eb5af6bf74cf5e8d729c4531d2bf","tid":1378493,"uid":181475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1457f16bebd6e49cb016d185807ec6f218dbdec1","tid":1378493,"uid":3234,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"青衣人，青衣係無得走<br />\n一封兩條橋邊到都唔洗去"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"青衣係有五條橋<br />\n昂船洲<br />\n汀九橋<br />\n青馬大橋<br />\n青衣南橋<br />\n青衣北橋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"長青隧道出口算唔算橋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"點落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271e6ba08ae76e014b4512e878a13bb7890e56ec","tid":1378493,"uid":6661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2185fac4054af974b2409726f5df84209653971d","tid":1378493,"uid":85694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"困獸鬥必死<br />\n而且係深藍區域"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"睇下青衣城1,2期中間個連儂牆就知唔藍得去邊"},{"pid":"41fb564ee7077825585ab6dc7e3def00725c48e3","tid":1378493,"uid":168472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70738fe420239e4e3fd3497c8b409a4975be90ca","tid":1378493,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"其實可以有兩條唔：<br />\n1，係美景花園ive果邊起點行去葵芳（南橋）<br />\n2，係青衣城青衣海旁果邊行去荃灣（北橋）<br />\n<br />\n咁行唔會俾狗封橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7a25f8545e2412ece53acc1f480287417c9305","tid":1378493,"uid":44139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70738fe420239e4e3fd3497c8b409a4975be90ca","tid":1378493,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"其實可以有兩條唔：<br />\n1，係美景花園ive果邊起點行去葵芳（南橋）<br />\n2，係青衣城青衣海旁果邊行去荃灣（北橋）<br />\n<br />\n咁行唔會俾狗封橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:32:19.000Z","msg":"雖然班狗痴左線，但青衣佢地第一時間都係諗到封橋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以比你夠時間行到都無用"}]}